frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers assembling a towering hamburger. The workers, clad in orange safety gear, are strategically positioned on ladders and scaffolding around the burger. The setting is a playful juxtaposition of construction and culinary art.
frames.description: The scene creatively combines elements of construction with food, showing tiny workers building a giant hamburger as if it were a skyscraper. This imaginative setting suggests a playful and humorous take on both construction and cooking.
